# Client Initialization

## Objective
Set up the `totem-view/client` application using Vue 3, Vite, and Tailwind CSS.

## Tasks
1. Create a new Vue 3 + TypeScript project using Vite inside `client/`.
2. Install and configure Tailwind CSS adhering to a standard modern design.
3. Remove boilerplate components and set up a clean `index.css` and `App.vue`.
4. Configure Vue Router for navigation (e.g., `/` for Dashboard).
